    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, ab eius nativitate
                        anno millesimo centesimo septuagesimo nono, quarto nonas decembris,
                        indictione tertiadecima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName>Albertinus
                            Marchesine</persName> et quondam <persName><name ref="Wiselbertus"
                                >Ghisalberti</name></persName> atque <persName><name ref="Saracinus"
                                >Saracinus</name></persName> eius filius et <persName><name
                                ref="Rimburghina">Rimburghina</name></persName> uxor suprascripti
                        Albertini atque <persName><name ref="Iolicta">Itta</name></persName> coniux
                        predicti Saracini quia, (…) ubi interesse videtur notitia <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Walandus">Gualandi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> donni imperatoris, (…) nos omnes insimul per
                        hanc cartulam vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominice</name></persName> rectori et custodi <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hospitalis</rs> de <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                                >Altepascio</placeName></orgName> (…) unam videlicet petiam de terra
                        que est campus cum arboribus et capanna super se, in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/2120">Tassignano</placeName> ubi dicitur
                        Valiano, prope <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3223"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> Beati Stephani</orgName>. Que tenet
                        ambo capita in viis publicis, latus unum tenet in terra et media fossa
                                <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberti</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidori</name></persName> et in terra et
                        media fossa <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3224">Sancti
                            Bartholomei</orgName>, alterum vero latus tenet in terra et media fossa
                                <persName><name ref="Briccus">Bricchi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Lambertuccius">Lambertucci</name></persName>
                        germanorum et in terra et media fossa <persName><name ref="Laborator"
                                >Laboratoris</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andree</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Findellus"
                                >Findelli</name></persName> germanorum quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Romanus">Romani</name></persName> et in terra et media fossa
                                <persName><name ref="Wizo">Guittonis</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Hughicio de Valiano">Ughicionis</name> de
                            Valiano</persName>. (…) <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: libras centum
                        quattuordecim et sol. decem et septem et denarios sex bonorum lucensium
                        denariorum. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et insuper sub penam
                        luc. <rs key="#Consules">consulum</rs> et treuguanorum presentium et
                        futurorum et lucensis <rs key="#Potestas">potestati</rs> que <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Consules #Potestas">Luce</placeName> pro tempore
                        fuerint, et centum lib. optimi argenti. (…) Hanc cartulam <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Deolofece">Deolofecui</name></persName> donni imperatoris
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarii</rs> scribere rogavimus. Actum Burgo Sancti Fridiani, in domo scilicet
                        suprascriptorum iugalium. (…). <rs key="#Witness">Testes</rs> <persName key="#Witness #Causidicus"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus de Sancto Andrea">Rolandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs> de Sancto Andrea, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gualtro">Gualtrone</name></persName> germanus suprascripti
                                <persName><name ref="Albertinus">Albertini</name></persName>,
                        <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Canamela">Cannamele</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Blancus">Blanchi</name></persName> qui
                        presentes rogati interfuere.</ab>
